Motschulsky, 1844: 92. Type locality: 
<normalizedToken id="8DA602D1A3C9A7DF3918F07624E88807" originalValue="«près">&quot;pres</normalizedToken>
de la redoute Yamyschevo non loin du fleuve Irtych [Siberia, Russia]&quot; (original citation). Holotype [by monotypy] in ZMMU (Keleinikova 1976: 202). Synonymy established by 
<normalizedToken id="3EC6AA069A2B7A3CE08B8BFFE5E5B49E" originalValue="Bänninger">Baenninger</normalizedToken>
(1930: 101).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6200F1F5258F4FD888360D90FD5F1D87" pageId="126" pageNumber="127">
